<p>It’s actually my sixtieth blog post, as I used to keep a tumblr.</p>

<p>Why I hate my birthday:</p>
<ul>
  <li>love? for me?! how dare you</li>
  <li>what have I done with my life?</li>
  <li>what am I doing with my life?</li>
</ul>

<p>Why I love my birthday:</p>
<ul>
  <li>my friends will come to my birthday party</li>
  <li>they will be happy</li>
  <li>steven warwick will sing me a song</li>
</ul>

